OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,FWords by ITV News Content Editor Jamie
OL,6,FSummers
OL,8,FAfter weeks of keeping a low profile
OL,9,Fwhile the war in the Middle East rages
OL,10,Fon, US Vice President JD Vance arrived
OL,11,Fin Budapest this week to show support
OL,12,Ffor Hungarian Prime Minister Viktor
OL,13,FOrban's re-election bid.
OL,15,FIt is a sign that Sunday's upcoming
OL,16,Fvote, in this small central European
OL,17,Fcountry of fewer than 10 million
OL,18,Fpeople, is the most significant
OL,19,Felection in Europe this year and will
OL,20,Fhave consequences across the world.
OL,26,@uD@Drp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
