OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,FIt matters because Orban, who has been
OL,6,Fin power for 16 years, is seen by many
OL,7,Fas the flag-bearer for right-wing
OL,8,Fpopulism in Europe. Crucially, he is a
OL,9,Fkey ally of both US President Donald
OL,10,FTrump and Russian President Vladimir
OL,11,FPutin.
OL,13,FBut after more than a decade of ruling
OL,14,Fwith huge majorities, Orban's grip on
OL,15,Fpower looks to be slipping.
OL,26,@mD@WrpvD@Zrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
