CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775657465
OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,FHis ruling Fidesz party have strong
OL,6,Finfluence over much of the country's
OL,7,Fmedia, but opinion polls suggest the
OL,8,Fopposition Tisza party is somewhere
OL,9,Fbetween eight and 20 points ahead just
OL,10,Fdays before the vote.
OL,12,FOrban has been Putin's staunchest `
OL,13,Fand often only - ally in the European
OL,14,FUnion since the outbreak of the war in
OL,15,FUkraine, and his government has
OL,16,Fconsistently frustrated the bloc's
OL,17,Fefforts to offer greater levels of
OL,18,Fsupport to Kyiv.
OL,26,@tD@Drp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
