OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775657465
OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,FBudapest has recently used its veto to
OL,6,Fblock the EU's proposed E90 billion
OL,7,F(#78 billion) relief loan to Ukraine.
OL,9,FHungary also remains heavily reliant
OL,10,Fon Russian oil and gas, increasing its
OL,11,Freliance while other EU countries have
OL,12,Fmoved away from imports to put
OL,13,Fpressure on Russia's ability to fund
OL,14,Fits war.
OL,16,FBut a series of domestic scandals has
OL,17,Fdented Orban's popularity in recent
OL,18,Fmonths. His period in power has been
OL,19,Faccompanied by a raft of anti-
OL,20,Fimmigration policies and restrictions
OL,21,Fon press freedom.
OL,26,@nD@YOkyD@Krp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
