OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,FLast year, his government made
OL,6,Finternational headlines when it
OL,7,Fcracked down on LGBT+ rights and
OL,8,Fbanned Pride marches ` leading to
OL,9,Fwidespread protests. Allegations of
OL,10,Fcorruption, which the government
OL,11,Fdenies, have further harmed its image.
OL,13,FThese and other issues have led to the
OL,14,Femergence of Peter Magyar and his
OL,15,FTisza party as a serious alternative
OL,16,Fto Orban.
OL,26,@xD@Grp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
