OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,FMagyar ` whose name means "Hungarian"
OL,6,Fin Hungarian ` is a former Fidesz
OL,7,Fmember turned Orban critic who is
OL,8,Friding a wave of popularity and using
OL,9,Fhis own conservative credentials to
OL,10,Fwoo former Orban voters.
OL,12,FOther opposition parties have spotted
OL,13,Fan opportunity to unseat Orban, and
OL,14,Falmost all of them have stepped aside
OL,15,Fto make it a two-horse race and
OL,16,Fmaximise Magyar's chances of victory.
OL,26,@oD@RrprD@OrpuD@]rp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
