OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,6,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,7,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,8,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,10,FFor its part, Orban's government has
OL,11,Fbeen accused by its critics of voter
OL,12,Fintimidation, using fake AI videos and
OL,13,Fmaking false claims about foreign
OL,14,Fplots to destabilise Hungary ` all of
OL,15,Fwhich they deny.
OL,17,FOne of the MPs standing aside in a bid
OL,18,Fto unify the opposition is David Bedo,
OL,19,Fwhose liberal Momentum party was one
OL,20,Fof the first to drop out of the race.
OL,26,@rD@RrpzD@]rpzD@e}w
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
