OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1775657465
OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,F"This is about regime change. The
OL,6,Fstandard of living is declining in
OL,7,Fthis country, and people are starting
OL,8,Fto notice. People in rural and
OL,9,Fcountryside areas where the Fidesz
OL,10,Fvote was strong are now turning away
OL,11,Ffrom them," he told ITV News.
OL,13,F"People may say it's a very unorthodox
OL,14,Fand irrational thing to drop out of
OL,15,Fthe race, but we're happy we made the
OL,16,Fdecision. The future is more
OL,17,Fimportant, and the outcome of this
OL,18,Felection will have an impact across
OL,19,Fthe whole of Europe."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
