OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,FWith the race entering its final days,
OL,6,Fboth major parties are criss-crossing
OL,7,FHungary, holding large-scale rallies
OL,8,Fto try to win over floating voters.
OL,10,FVance's appearance in Budapest is an
OL,11,Findication of how high the Trump
OL,12,Fadministration sees the stakes for one
OL,13,Fof MAGA's biggest European allies.
OL,15,FAnd it's not just in the US where this
OL,16,Fresult will be watched closely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
