OL,3,CWhy Hungary's election matters
OL,5,FRight-wing and far-right parties are
OL,6,Fpolling strongly across Europe,
OL,7,Fincluding the National Rally, which is
OL,8,Fattempting to win the French
OL,9,Fpresidency next year ` and they will
OL,10,Fbe eyeing closely what happens in
OL,11,FHungary.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, other leaders across Europe
OL,14,Fawait the result to see whether
OL,15,FHungary will once again re-elect
OL,16,FOrban, or turn instead to his pro-EU,
OL,17,Fpro-western rival.
OL,19,FEither way, this election will have
OL,20,Fhuge ramifications far beyond
OL,21,FHungary's borders.
